latestPosts.caption:
A month ago, @salimmerchant @priyism told me there’s a chance that I may get to sing with @zedd and today we’re here — @priyism @bcmanju and 7 beautiful voices - @aasa.sing @kamadiorama @alvina._.dsouza @darshanamenon @nikitha_venkatesh @saptakchatterjeeofficial @adityakalway ❤️

Thank you @lollaindia for a memory of a lifetime 🫶🏻

CEO at @merchant_records, yes - @salimmerchant and @sulaiman.merchant sirs really gave me the “pankh” to fly 🕊️

Merchant Records has always been an artist-driven label and it shows. I never thought I would be where I am today - at 24 years old, taking on the role of CEO at a record label. 

Bringing together my love for music and entrepreneurship is probably the best thing that has happened to me lately. From that one Instagram Live Video to releasing my first song with Sirs to here - so much has happened and so much is ready to unfold. 

Having my parents, my friends, and the entire MR family by my side has been my core strength. I’m what I am today because of all of them.

Here’s to the future and all the amazing music we’re going to create together! Can’t wait to see where this takes me.

#CEO #MerchantRecords #SalimSulaiman #ShivanshJindal #PankhoKo #Explore #DreamComeTrue #Entrepreneurship
